---
const symptoms = [
  {
    text: "You wake up exhausted, even after a full night's sleep",
  },
  {
    text: "You're irritable with the people you love most",
  },
  {
    text: "You feel guilty for not being more grateful for your success",
  },
  {
    text: "You've lost interest in things that used to excite you",
  },
  {
    text: "You're running on autopilot, going through the motions",
  },
  {
    text: "You wonder if this is all there is",
  },
];
---

<section id="symptoms" class="symptoms-section">
  <div class="container">
    <header class="symptoms-header" data-reveal>
      <span class="section-subtitle">Recognition</span>
      <h2 class="section-title balance">Is this you?</h2>
      <p class="symptoms-intro">
        You've done everything right. The career, the title, the respect. And yet...
      </p>
    </header>

    <ul class="symptoms-list">
      {symptoms.map((symptom, index) => (
        <li
          class="symptom-item"
          data-reveal
          style={`transition-delay: ${index * 100}ms`}
        >
          <span class="symptom-marker"></span>
          <span class="symptom-text">{symptom.text}</span>
        </li>
      ))}
    </ul>

    <div class="symptoms-footer" data-reveal>
      <p class="symptoms-reassurance">
        If you recognize yourself in these words, you're not alone. And you're not broken.
        <strong>You're simply running a system that was never designed to run this hard, for this long.</strong>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Breathing line divider -->
  <div class="section-divider">
    <div class="divider-breathing"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .symptoms-section {
    padding: var(--space-2xl) 0;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
  }

  .symptoms-header {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    display: block;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: var(--weight-semibold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-widest);
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    font-weight: var(--weight-normal);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .symptoms-intro {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
  }

  .symptoms-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .symptom-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    padding: var(--space-md);
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: all var(--duration-normal) var(--ease-calm);
  }

  .symptom-item:hover {
    border-color: var(--border-hover);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .symptom-marker {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    margin-top: 8px;
    background: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .symptom-text {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: var(--leading-snug);
  }

  .symptoms-footer {
    max-width: 650px;
  }

  .symptoms-reassurance {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
  }

  .symptoms-reassurance strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .section-divider {
    padding-top: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .symptom-item {
      padding: var(--space-sm);
    }

    .symptom-text {
      font-size: var(--text-base);
    }
  }
</style>
